                Automated workflows guide customers through critical setup steps systematically, reducing average time-to-first-value from <strong class="text-primary">45 days to 13 days</strong> across typical SaaS implementations. These workflows often integrate with <a href="/blog/ai-powered-knowledge-base-software" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 underline">AI-powered knowledge base systems</a> to provide contextual help and documentation throughout the onboarding journey.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
