              <ul class="text-black space-y-2">
                <li><strong>Over-automation:</strong> Maintain human touchpoints for complex or high-value customers</li>
                <li><strong>Generic experiences:</strong> Implement proper segmentation from day one</li>
                <li><strong>Poor timing:</strong> Space communications appropriately to avoid overwhelming customers</li>
